depois disso ?

246
00:15:56,620 --> 00:15:57,820
Quando ?

247
00:15:57,860 --> 00:16:00,100
Na outra vida.

248
00:16:00,180 --> 00:16:02,300
Naquela que nos espera
depois da nossa morte.

249
00:16:02,340 --> 00:16:04,300
Sabe para onde vocês iriam ?

250
00:16:04,340 --> 00:16:05,540
Ahh.

251
00:16:05,580 --> 00:16:07,140
Sabe onde, Nicholas ?

252
00:16:07,220 --> 00:16:08,740
