para brincar com a gente.

423
00:25:34,940 --> 00:25:36,140
Nicholas!

424
00:25:36,180 --> 00:25:40,260
Huh ?
O que ?

425
00:25:40,300 --> 00:25:42,940
Olhe.

426
00:25:42,980 --> 00:25:44,900
